## Formatting

- One idea per line. Every time.
- Hook must stand alone in 2 lines of mobile preview.
- No bullet points in the post body — short sentences instead.
- Visuals: always include one when possible. Even a crop, a detail, or a WIP screenshot beats text alone.
- 2–3 hashtags at the very end. Core digital designer tags: #DigitalDesign #GraphicDesign #MarketingDesign
- Emojis: 0–2 max if the designer's tone calls for them, zero if they prefer clean.

